datasets.name: 50ac2232
queryLines:
SELECT * FROM main.uc_workflow_scoping.sample 
WHERE 
( 
    (:job_id = 'all' AND :latest_name = 'all' )
    OR
    ( :job_id <> 'all' AND :latest_name = 'all'
    AND job_id = CAST(:job_id AS string) )
    OR
    ( :job_id = 'all' AND :latest_name <> 'all'
    AND latest_name = CAST(:latest_name AS string) )
    OR
    ( :job_id <> 'all' AND :latest_name <> 'all'
    AND job_id = CAST(:job_id AS string) 
    AND latest_name = CAST(:latest_name AS string) 
     )

datasets.name: 1d37fce0
queryLines:
SELECT job_id, latest_name, list_cost
FROM main.uc_workflow_scoping.sample
ORDER BY list_cost DESC
LIMIT 10

datasets.name: b6eb89b1
datasets.displayName: Top 10 Workflows by Count of Runs
queryLines:
SELECT job_id, latest_name, Total_Runs
FROM main.uc_workflow_scoping.sample
WHERE latest_name != 'continuous job with vacuum'
ORDER BY total_runs DESC
LIMIT 10

datasets.name: f36ae318
queryLines:
SELECT *, date_diff(latest_execution_time, created_date) AS Workflow_Age FROM main.uc_workflow_scoping.sample
ORDER BY Workflow_Age DESC
LIMIT 10

datasets.name: 2b2e60e2
datasets.displayName: Top 10 Workflows by Runs in Last Quarter
queryLines:
SELECT * 
FROM main.uc_workflow_scoping.sample
WHERE latest_name != 'continuous job with vacuum'
ORDER BY q2_2025_runs DESC
LIMIT 10
